public class ThirdPartyDeviceProviderMsgDefines.RxOnlyAPI.CommandMessage
extends java.lang.Object

Defines the command messages allowed required in this interface to control the device. Sent from the client to the provider over the ThirdPartyDeviceProviderMsgDefines.DeviceAccessRequest.RequestAccess_ResponseMessage.PARAM_GRANT_msgrCOMMANDRECEIVER.
